Django / Pandas / Plotly project from scratch.

To create a project :
django-admin startproject Django_Plotly

To create an app (for example "main" app) :
python manage.py startapp main
add app in settings/INSTALLED_APPS

DÃ©pendances : 
pip install -r requirement.txt

To launch the developpement server :
python manage.py runserver

** Admin **
Create a superuser
python manage.py createsuperuser

** Model **
When new model is created :
python manage.py makemingrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py migrate --run-syncdb

register the model in app/admin.py 

** git **
git status
git commit -m 'name of commit'
git push origin master